<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong>“冬之恋”系列音乐会</strong><strong> </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">2012年11月18日   晚19:30<br /></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">地点：民族音乐厅<br /></span><br />主持人：王军（国家一级演员）<br /></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: medium;">钢琴伴奏：全艳  张小铄</span> </span></p>
 
<p><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">一、女声独唱《一杯美酒》                                                                新疆民歌</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                 《采茶舞曲》                                                           周大风词曲</span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                演唱：赵娜</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、男高音独唱《阳光路上》                                 甲丁 王晓岭词  张宏光曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                    《怀念战友》                                                        雷振邦词曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                    《在那遥远的地方》                                            王洛宾词曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                          演唱：张向华 （文化部优秀剧目展演获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、二胡独奏《雪山魂塑》                                                                刘文金曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                               演奏：康娅妮</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、女声独唱《洗菜心》                                                                湖南花鼓戏</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                 </span>《溜溜的竹排溜溜的漂》                                 林澍词  伍林曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                               演唱：唐文娟</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、男低音独唱《多情的土地》                                       任志萍词 施光南曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                     《我为祖国献石油》                             薛柱国词  秦咏诚曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                     《夕阳红》                                                 乔羽词  张丕基曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                                演唱：赵健</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、女高音独唱《祖国啊，我永远热爱你》                       刘合庄词 李正曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                    </span></span>《西班牙女郎》                                                    意大利民歌</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                    </span></span>《我像雪花天上来》                                  晓光词  徐沛东曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                             演唱：龚俊莉</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、男声独唱《乌苏里船歌》                                                        赫哲族民歌</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                 </span>《江山》                                                              晓光词 印青曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                              演唱：尤龙</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、琵琶独奏《十面埋伏》                                                                        古曲</span><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                           演奏：尹秋薇</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: medium;">九、女中音独唱《我们的祖国歌甜花香》                          王持久词  郭峰曲<br /><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                    </span>《吐鲁番的葡萄熟了》                              瞿琮词  施光南曲</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                    </span>《我和我的祖国》                                      张藜词  秦咏诚曲</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                 演唱：吴玫玫（国家一级演员）</span></span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十、男女声二重唱《想亲亲》                                                             山西民歌<br /><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                        </span></span>《龙船调》                                                            湖北民歌</span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                      演唱：唐文娟  尤龙</span><br /></span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: medium;">十</span></span><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-size: medium;">一、女高音独唱《曙色》                                                   晓光词  徐沛东曲<br /><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                        </span></span>《云河》                                                            刘家昌词曲<br /></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: medium;">                                        《玛依拉变奏曲》                                             胡廷江改编</span></span></span><br /><span style="font-size: medium;">                                                 演唱：谢琳（国家一级演员）</span><br /></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: medium;"><br /><br /><br /> 注：曲目如有变动，请以演出当日为准。                   [2012-A-028]</span></span></p>
